{"tid":1947269,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隔籬手帶app 「居安抗疫」 原來係由科大d公司開發","createTime":"2020-03-28T07:36:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T16:39:09.000Z","uid":263197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"565d87efe870bad7146d49a5f9102e86b526bbdc","tid":1947269,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"由<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">科大計算機科學及工程學系兼創業中心主任陳雙幸教授</span></span>領導的一支研究團隊，開發了一種自動化地理圍欄技術「Signature Home」。科大將有關技術的特許使用權授予一間<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">初創公司「隨賞科技</span></span>」，並透過該公司開發一個新手機應用程式<span style=\"color: gold;\">「居安抗疫」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n陳教授此前發明的另一種室內定位技術，現已透過隨賞科技被廣泛應用到<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大灣區</span></span>的大型購物中心和醫院當中。<br />\n<br />\n由陳教授於<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2015年創立</span></span>的隨賞科技，在室內定位技術領域具領先地位。該公司曾獲多個獎項，亦在孵化期間透過大學科技初創企業資助計劃，取得科大的財務支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ust.hk/zh-hant/news/research-and-innovation/hkust-researchers-develop-smart-geo-fencing-technology-home-quarantine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ust.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fnews%2Fresearch-and-innovation%2Fhkust-researchers-develop-smart-geo-fencing-technology-home-quarantine&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq7yGpUrO7QrNXIpVIwIXQug%3D&h=5150c199\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ust.hk/zh-hant/news/research-and-innovation/hkust-researchers-develop-smart-geo-fencing-technology-home-quarantine</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n公司pages<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gunz7pf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fgunz7pf.jpg&h=aa93186f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://kt.ust.hk/zh-hant/startups/隨賞科技有限公司\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkt.ust.hk%2Fzh-hant%2Fstartups%2F%E9%9A%A8%E8%B3%9E%E7%A7%91